li.span: After Disable LPM, the current measurement value of the product cannot reach the expected current value.
DUT can't be detect/program at YAMS1 or YAMS2.

span.div: DG1 will provide these hardware and help setup this tester.

ol.li: Send a I2C command to disable DUT LPM through Arduino,
Read the current measurement value of the programmable power supply to see whether the current value of the DUT is within the expected current value range.

li.span: If it is not within the range, the PCBA is judged to “FAIL”.
Otherwise, the PCBA is initially considered to be good.
